Method Parameters:-->
		=> Method parameters carry runtime data to methods.
		=> Method parameters change state of method behavior
			at runtime
		
		Advantages:-->
		=> Without hard code programs we can reuse
			methods with different input data
			
	Parameters are available in two types.
	
		=>callByvalue    [passing parameters as datatypes ]
						 [String,int,boolean ---etc]
						 
		=>callByreference[Passing classes as parameters]
						 [classes,Interfac --etc]
		
		
		
			
		